== 評論 ==
「和平佔中」秘書處不滿「佔中後援會」的名字相近，讓市民誤以為佔中後援會的論述是和平佔中的立場，遂發公開聲明橫清界線。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://oclp.hk/index.php?route=occupy/activity_detail&activity_id=30| title=「和平佔中」聲明：澄清坊間無冠名之「佔中後援會」並不隸屬「和平佔中」| publisher=「讓愛與和平佔領中環」官方網頁| access-date=2019-10-22| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812142445/http://oclp.hk/index.php?route=occupy%2Factivity_detail&activity_id=30| archive-date=2017-08-12| dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20131203/00176_091.html| title=「快必騎劫佔中」| newspaper=東方日報| date=2013-12-03| accessdate=2015-06-11| archive-date=2016-03-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304210202/http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20131203/00176_091.html| dead-url=no}}</ref> 一直反對「佔領中環」運動的[[黃洋達|黃洋達]]、[[熱血公民|熱血公民]]亦連翻揶揄、攻擊佔中後援會。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-15-2013/6306| title=多舊魚的「佔中後援會」| publisher=[[熱血時報|熱血時報]]| date=2013-11-15| author=陳到| accessdate=2017-05-16| archive-date=2017-08-12| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812141723/http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-15-2013/6306| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://passiontimes.hk/article/12-04-2013/6747| author=陳四| title=佔中後援會的司馬懿之心，路人皆見| publisher=[[熱血時報|熱血時報]]| date=2013-12-04| accessdate=2017-05-16| archive-date=2017-08-12| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812141258/http://passiontimes.hk/article/12-04-2013/6747| dead-url=no}}</ref>

更有評論員指責「佔中後援會」在民主黨宣誓佔中之時抗議、搗亂，是配合建制派、親政府力量去攻擊「和平佔中」為暴力行為。<ref>[http://www.post852.com/6497/%E5%8A%89%E7%9A%87%E7%99%BC%E6%B1%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%96%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%80%E3%80%8C%E6%BF%80%E9%80%B2%E6%B4%BE%E3%80%8D%E7%82%BA%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E3%80%8C%E9%96%8B%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%8D/ 〈劉皇發污名化佔中　「激進派」為民主黨「開路」？〉] {{Wayback|url=http://www.post852.com/6497/%E5%8A%89%E7%9A%87%E7%99%BC%E6%B1%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%96%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%80%E3%80%8C%E6%BF%80%E9%80%B2%E6%B4%BE%E3%80%8D%E7%82%BA%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E3%80%8C%E9%96%8B%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%8D/ |date=20170812143142 }}，《852郵報》，2014年2月6日。</ref>

